@startuml
skinparam monochrome true
skinparam shadowing true
[*] --> Pending
Pending --> Created : update
Pending : entry / log card
Created --> Completed : confirm
Completed --> Reviewed : review
Reviewed --> Cancelled : approve
Reviewed : entry / log card
Cancelled --> Approved : submit
Cancelled : entry / log card
Cancelled --> Reviewed : revert
Approved --> [*]
@enduml